class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kcb1665702670762.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kcb1665702670762.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kcb1665702670762.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kcb1665702670762\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls the position of logical printers in the Microsoft Windows\n    registry.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__topic_d145712e1_d145713e1_d145714e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__p_d145715e1_d145716e1_d145717e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Registry_Style</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">BY_VERSION</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">BY_APSNAME</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__section_w4x_qkq_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d412211e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__ul_rhk_rkq_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__li_d50720e1_d50721e1_d50722e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BY_VERSION</code>—default, if\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Registry_Style</span> is not specified. The resulting registry entry is: <p class=\"p\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__p_d145721e1_d145722e1_d145723e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Uniface/Uniface</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Version</var>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__li_d50723e1_d50724e1_d50725e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BY_APSNAME</code>—key the registry by\n          application name. The resulting registry entry is: <p class=\"p\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__p_d145724e1_d145725e1_d145726e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Uniface/Uniface</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Version</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/logprinter/</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ApsName</var>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__table_d17768e1_d17769e1_d17770e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BY_VERSION</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vas1665702670549.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vas1665702670549.html\" title=\"The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions.\">[printer]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcb1665702670762__p_d145727e1_d145728e1_d145729e1\">When you use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Registry_Style</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= BY_APSNAME</code>, an extra copy of the registry key will be placed in the\n        default position. This is a result of the default behavior that moves all registry settings\n        to the default location. These extra logical printer keys do not influence run-time\n        behavior.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vas1665702670549.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[printer]</a><p>The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Registry_Style Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls the position of logical printers in the Microsoft Windows registry. Registry_Style { = } BY_VERSION | BY_APSNAME Arguments BY_VERSION —default, if Registry_Style is not specified. The resulting registry entry is: HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Uniface/Uniface Version BY_APSNAME —key the registry by application name. The resulting registry entry is: HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Uniface/Uniface Version /logprinter/ ApsName Default value BY_VERSION File section [printer] When you use Registry_Style = BY_APSNAME , an extra copy of the registry key will be placed in the default position. This is a result of the default behavior that moves all registry settings to the default location. These extra logical printer keys do not influence run-time behavior. Related Links [printer] The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}